{"tid":557273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狂男北京商場斬人 至少1死4傷特警封鎖現場","createTime":"2018-02-11T07:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T12:46:49.000Z","uid":122,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"707f904b6d97e5c7eda3aadf5006219f23bdb910","tid":557273,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T07:45:31.000Z","msg":"北京鬧市發生斬人案，西城區西單大悅城商場有一名男子持刀斬人，大批民眾慌忙走避，上留有血迹，警方趕到場後將男子制服，傷者已經送院，現場消息指最少有1死4傷。<br />\n<br />\n據目擊網友稱，「我們被封鎖在施華洛世奇店裏，店員很慌張，結賬都結巴了。外面擔架抬走第4個人了，還有很多人朝出口奔跑，扶梯已經不能用了，很多特警封鎖了現場。也有很多被砍傷的人捂着頭向前走，聽說這波人轉砍脖子和頭。真是刀刀致命。」<br />\n<br />\n另有網友描述：「大家全跑出來了，嚇得我到現在還渾身發抖。有個女孩好像被砍傷脖子後面，男朋友一直在叫救護車，另外一個女孩被砍傷耳朵，地上血迹很多&hellip;&hellip;」有人受傷後現場亂成一團，大批民眾四處狂奪，「我跟同學上去的時候一群人往下衝」，小童被嚇至大哭，現場一片混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180211/57820097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180211%2F57820097&d=XcvNY2S5fmIe3NJrS%2F6R9bIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=ec11f5ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180211%2F57820097&h=392f73ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180211/57820097</a>"},{"pid":"769bf66f996c88caa648f64c2909683468a9100c","tid":557273,"uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T07:47:02.000Z","msg":"還有黨呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2016d8c01c101fe4501ecdc62cee07f2ecc382f0","tid":557273,"uid":61954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T08:30:41.000Z","msg":"咁快開年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7710e7fa40383759c53adc7e2c7b503f7d09f8","tid":557273,"uid":162424,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T08:33:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c1d3eac22b56d10a0d9f87859c4a7e0ef8c8edd","tid":557273,"uid":26752,